headline: Occidental Petroleum Could Hike Its Dividend - Price Target is At Least 21% Higher
summary: Occidental Petroleum is likely to raise its dividend next quarter. At $1.00 per share, OXY would yield 2.32%. Based on its historical average, OXY stock could be worth $50, which could be 21% higher.
